        <div class="home-banner-image-hover">
          <span><%= user.artist_name %></span>
          <div class="home-banner-image-hover-token">
            <% project = Project.find_by(user_id: user) %>
            <span><%= project.number_of_tokens - project.number_of_transactions(project) %></span>
            <span>Tokens left</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-banner-image booba">
        <% user = User.find_by(artist_name: "Booba") %>
        <div class="home-banner-image-name opacity"><%= user.artist_name %></div>
        <div class="home-banner-image-hover">
          <span><%= user.artist_name %></span>
          <div class="home-banner-image-hover-token">
            <% project = Project.find_by(user_id: user) %>
            <span><%= project.number_of_tokens - project.number_of_transactions(project) %></span>
            <span>Tokens left</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-banner-image peggy-gou">
        <% user = User.find_by(artist_name: "Peggy Gou") %>
        <div class="home-banner-image-name opacity"><%= user.artist_name %></div>
        <div class="home-banner-image-hover">
          <span><%= user.artist_name %></span>
          <div class="home-banner-image-hover-token">
            <% project = Project.find_by(user_id: user) %>
            <span><%= project.number_of_tokens - project.number_of_transactions(project) %></span>
            <span>Tokens left</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-features">
    <h2>Invest on <span class="banner-highlight-primary">tomorrow's artists</span></h2>
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="home-features-sml col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <%= image_tag("home-feature-1.svg")%>
        <h3>Discover  artists</h3>
        <p>Discover tomorrow's artists depending on the artist's name,
        genre or anticipated generated revenue.</p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-home" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample1">
            See more
          </a>
        </p>
        <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample1">
          <div class="card card-body text-justify">
            Artists have huge costs associated with launching new albums, singles or EPs. <br><br>They need to advance money to cover music videos, promotions or any other associated costs before generating a single penny of revenue, which makes it very hard to succeed in the music industry. <br><br>Support artists you like or want to see succeed by investing in their musical projects.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-features-sml col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <%= image_tag("home-feature-2.svg")%>
        <h3>Invest in their projects</h3>
        <p>Take advantage of our secture platform to invest in
        an artist's project to finance their upcoming hits.</p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-home" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample2" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample2">
            See more
          </a>
        </p>
        <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample2">
          <div class="card card-body text-justify">
            To invest in the projects, Geyoshares has decided to implement a token system. <br><br>An artist can choose to divide the projects in three different shares: the artist’s shares, the distributor’s shares and the investor’s shares, which are up for sale on this website. <wbr>

            <br><br>Each token has a value of 0.1% of the total project, meaning there are a 1000 tokens up for sale per project. In other words, for one token purchased, an investor will earn 0.1% of the future revenue stream. <br>

            <br><br>The price per token varies for each project and is determined by the artists themselves based on the calculated estimated revenues. These metrics will allow you to invest in projects in a transparent manner.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="home-features-sml col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <%= image_tag("home-feature-3.svg")%>
        <h3>Become rich</h3>
        <p>Beneficiate  from a high return on investment
        on your<br> projects.</p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-home " data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample3" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample3">
            See more
          </a>
        </p>
        <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample3">
          <div class="card card-body text-justify color-white">
            Thanks to solid and transparent partnerships with distributors, earnings will be redistributed monthly, based on the artist’s generated revenues.<br><br>On this basis, investors will gain from a rapid return on investment.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


